data.description: Step inside this charming Cape Cod with new handrails and shutters to discover wood look tile floors throughout. The kitchen features hickory butcher block countertops, custom shaker panel cabinet doors, a farmhouse sink, tile backsplash, wrap-around floating shelves adorned with ambient lighting, and is equipped with newer appliances (dishwasher, electric range, range hood, French door refrigerator). Enjoy meals at the custom kitchen nook with table. The adjacent living space boasts a custom TV mantle with an electric fireplace insert. The bedrooms offer an array of built-ins including dressers in knee walls, headboard with lights and electrical outlets, bookcase with dresser and queen-sized Murphy bed. The primary bath has retiled shower walls & custom niche, a new steel tub, a Bluetooth shower fan/speaker, glass door, and a rain shower system. String lights, Bluetooth speakers, and a 120v hot tub set the mood on the back patio surrounded by a new wood privacy fence.
